{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "Medicano API",
    "description": "Coleção completa da API Medicano.\n\nVariáveis de coleção preenchidas automaticamente via scripts:\n- token: após login ou signup\n- clinicId, professionalId, patientId, appointmentId, sessionId, subscriptionId, attendantId, userId\n\nFluxo recomendado:\n1. Auth → Signup (patient) → Login automático\n2. Auth → Signup (clinic) → Login → Clinics → Create Clinic\n3. Professionals → Create Professional\n4. Clinics → Professionals → Assign Professional to Clinic\n5. Subscriptions → Create Subscription (para aparecer na busca)\n6. Search → Search\n7. Appointments → Create Appointment\n8. Chat → Create Session → Send Message",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",        "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token",          "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "clinicId",       "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "professionalId", "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "patientId",      "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "appointmentId",  "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "sessionId",      "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "subscriptionId", "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "attendantId",    "value": "",                      "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId",         "value": "",                      "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Signup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.accessToken);",
                  "if (res.user?._id) pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', res.user._id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"role\": \"patient\",\n  \"name\": \"João Silva\",\n  \"email\": \"joao@exemplo.com\",\n  \"password\": \"senha1234\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/signup", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "signup"] },
            "description": "role: patient | clinic | professional\n\nRetorna accessToken — salvo automaticamente na variável 'token'."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (padrão)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.accessToken);",
                  "if (res.user?._id) pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', res.user._id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"joao@exemplo.com\",\n  \"password\": \"senha1234\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] },
            "description": "Roles: patient, clinic, professional.\n\nToken salvo automaticamente."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (atendente)",
